{"tid":517252,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"依家啲茶餐廳係咪出前一丁都唔識煮?","createTime":"2018-01-02T06:37:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-02T06:43:24.000Z","uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ed914b6bdfce292aadc4ba30dcb0663158a40e17","tid":517252,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T06:37:45.000Z","msg":"10間有7間都係掉舊一丁落滾水就上<br />\n結果一丁就成塊未熟<br />\n湯就熱到燙口又咸到仆街<br />\n仲衰過自己淥<br />\n<br />\n細個好多茶餐廳仲用扁平碟上嗰陣好食好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"141562646f113333de8716d3d96e56dea6b0f6e5","tid":517252,"uid":145247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T06:38:19.000Z","msg":"Agger <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"172600ff2ce9e46d6c9c22aa7666d2e33e86f5e0","tid":517252,"uid":59465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T06:39:52.000Z","msg":"平碟上嘅多數大光麵嚟<br />\n一丁多數都碗上<br />\n咁多年嚟都係咁"},{"pid":"6e62d9690eb2a883cc9225d87a31ad4f89e21812","tid":517252,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T06:40:01.000Z","msg":"無心左好多係真<br />\n有D仆街夠膽死用返蛋麵個湯比你,根本變左第二樣野<br />\n一係就多水過頭,個湯啖到仆街<br />\n加3,4蚊食屎,中過伏既唔會再去"},{"pid":"5a92d385d3e0536521eeb4411a8d0f655ad6b24e","tid":517252,"uid":59465,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T06:40:38.000Z","msg":"不過最好食嘅茶記公仔麵<br />\n一定係用忌廉湯做湯底<br />\n個隻真係超好食<br />\n不過買少見少了"},{"pid":"1deeb74bc3b2030719bcf0d897de714528f9d0df","tid":517252,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a92d385d3e0536521eeb4411a8d0f655ad6b24e","tid":517252,"uid":59465,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T06:40:38.000Z","msg":"不過最好食嘅茶記公仔麵<br />\n一定係用忌廉湯做湯底<br />\n個隻真係超好食<br />\n不過買少見少了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T06:43:09.000Z","msg":"你講哩樣, 我諗就係我印象中嗰種<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"